^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Well defense could have beat it one more, but this is fine. The auction needs discussion. Kerrie's 2H bid was very aggressive, particularly vulnerable. It happened to work out well, again proving that aggressiveness often pays off. However, she only has 5 mediocre hearts, she is vul, and we have not found a fit. So, 2H is extremely risky. In general, on this auction, with her hand, I recommend against it. |
