NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|But, let us assume 2H was bid. With my singleton heart, and six diamonds, I felt 3D was merited. And by The Law, Eddy has a clear 3H bid. Let us now discuss Nada's options. It is true she has six spades. However, they are very bad spades, and I did not raise. I might very well have raised with 3 to an honor. She has a singleton in my suit and she has points in their suit. On this hand, she clearly wants to defend. We could easily be beating the hand with the Ace of diamonds, a ruff, another heart to start with.|
