NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|On this hand, in particular, with no wasted diamond cards, your hand is even better. Now, one other comment. 1N over 1D without a diamond stopper is a bit of a problem. On the other hand, Roberta has no good bid. You could argue for pass, or 1N. Double would be a problem. Marty Bergen would recommend 1N with Roberta's hand (only over a minor opening) so she is in good company. Bergen says with a 1N overcall point-wise and no other good bid, it is ok to overcall 1N witn no minor suit stopper. I think 1N was ok as well. Either pass or 1N works for me.|
