^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Interesting hand to bid and play. I had a problem  with my hand. I have 3 choices of bids, all of which are imperfect. I could overcall 1N to show my points. I have some diamond stoppers as even if partner has Jxx I have a stopper. I could overcall 2C, but my club suit is not that great. Or I could double. Generally, with 2 unbid majors, my rule is that you need to be at least 4-3. Since I am only 3-3, I would have to violate that rule. But, since my major suit holdings are so good, I decided it was ok to make a takeout double, as I have really excellent 3 card support for either major.|
